excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月中旬，西部某地方性银行的客户经理赵佳收到了当月的工资——底薪加上绩效，再扣除每年固定的五险一金，到手的不足 1000 元。上个月，这个数字是 2000 多。此前，她的月薪可以过万。 2023 年以来，人们对银行业降薪的讨论日趋激烈。在某社交平台上，「银行降薪」的话题有近百万次浏览，有网友说，他已经经历了两轮降薪，平均月薪从 8000 元下降到了 4000 元。 Wind 数据显示，2023 年，42 家 A 股上市银行中，共有 14 家上市银行人均薪酬下降，最大降幅达 13.95%。 多家上市银行「反向讨薪」也引发市场关注。据澎湃新闻此前报道，截至今年 3 月末，至少 7 家上市银行披露了去年绩效薪酬追索扣回的具体情况，追索回扣金额合计 5280.97 万元。（澎湃新闻记者 林倩冰）银行业降薪遭热议：银行客户经理月薪从过万降至到手不足 1000_ 股上市 _ 绩效 _ 薪酬"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-161ffc87d5e65b2db970b0aba08377b4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "121 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/656797343"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8Ij22sHJuPVSEAMaCTEwODIzMzA4MSDC0bWyBjAAOD1ABnIJNjU2Nzk3MzQzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1716429061.404456", "card_id": "Q_656309128", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《庆余年第二季》被换掉的几个角色中，谁最让人惋惜？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-608bd21710d9f7e0c69dd78384036d01_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "119 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/656309128"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8Ij22sHJuPVSEAMaCTEwODEyNDI3NyCLsJyyBjAAOC1AB3IJNjU2MzA5MTI4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1716429061.404737", "card_id": "Q_656860236", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https: